From Verve Records comes this live performance by renowned pianist Oscar Peterson. Backed by the Danish bassist Niels-Henning Orsted Pedersen, guitarist Ulf Wakenius, and drummer Martin Drew, Peterson performs such songs as "Falling in Love With Love," "When Summer Comes," "Cakewalk," "The Backyard Blues," and "Sweet Georgia Brown."
